Your childcare service account

JULIE SMITH

Manage the account

I'm new to the childcare service, what do I do first?

You should go to:

  • your secure messages to check your eligibility response
  • Free Childcare For Working Parents to view and start using your code
  • Your Tax-Free Childcare account to pay money in, add and pay childcare providers

Manage your Tax-Free Childcare account, pay money in and select and pay childcare providers

View your Free Childcare For Working Parents codes

View messages about your application and account

View or change your email address or phone number

Confirm your details are up to date every 3 months. Do this between 19 January 2025 and 15 February 2025

I've missed my end date, what do I do?
You can still reconfirm, but the amount of government support you get may be less if you weren't eligible for the full 3 months.

Reset your telephone password, change and view your security check questions

Apply for a new child, or one who wasn't eligible in an earlier application

View your last application or reconfirmation summary
